OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091066
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F'Sarah' is still traumatised by the
OL,8,Fincident, which saw a drunk member of
OL,9,Fthe public easily get hold of a
OL,10,Fkeycard to her room, as Good Morning
OL,11,FBritain Correspondent Ashna Hurynag
OL,12,Freports
OL,14,FA woman who had her room accessed by a
OL,15,Fstranger with a key card has been left
OL,16,Ftraumatised, after he barged in on her
OL,17,Fnaked although she had locked the door.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F'Sarah', whose identity we are
OL,8,Fprotecting, had been staying in a
OL,9,FTravelodge in York in June 2025 for a
OL,10,Fwork conference.
OL,12,FShe had finished for the day and was
OL,13,Flooking forward to a relaxing evening,
OL,14,Fbut was harassed in the lobby as she
OL,15,Fwas heading up to her room
OL,17,F"There's a group of men in fancy
OL,18,Fdress, they've been drinking and
OL,19,Fthey're making comments to me and
OL,20,Fwhistling, saying, I'm sexy," she
OL,21,Frecalled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F"One of them said in my face - 'You
OL,8,Fare so gorgeous'."
OL,10,FShe ignored them and went up to her
OL,11,Froom: "I just sort of rolled my eyes.
OL,12,FI went up to my room, but I heard him
OL,13,Fshout my room number to his friend,
OL,14,Fthat worried me, so I locked the door."
OL,16,FSarah rang her husband who put her
OL,17,Fmind at ease, and began to get ready
OL,18,Fto have a bath.
OL,20,FBut as she was undressed, the door
OL,21,Fswung open.
OL,26,@sD@GOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F"I'm about to go in the bath, and that
OL,8,Fsame man who told me I was gorgeous,
OL,9,Fentered my room," she said.
OL,11,F"He opened the door, and I screamed so
OL,12,Floud. I ran forward and was able to
OL,13,Fshut the door on him, but he didn't
OL,14,Fleave. He was on the other side of the
OL,15,Fdoor, telling me to be quiet, telling
OL,16,Fme to calm down. And I just kept
OL,17,Fscreaming."
OL,19,FSarah was utterly distraught, and so
OL,20,Fterrified she had a panic attack.
OL,26,@yD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,FThere was no phone in the room, so she
OL,8,Fsearched for the number online and
OL,9,Ftried to call reception three times.
OL,10,FThere was no answer so she rang the
OL,11,Fpolice.
OL,13,FThe police operator consoled her and
OL,14,Fasked her to stay on the line as she
OL,15,Fgot dressed and went down to reception.
OL,17,FGobsmacked, she demanded to know how
OL,18,Fthe individual had managed to get a
OL,19,Fkey to her room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F"He, he just asked for it. He just
OL,8,Fwent to reception and said, 'Can I
OL,9,Fhave a key for this number?' And they
OL,10,Fknew he was a guest at the hotel,
OL,11,Fbecause they'd seen him, and they just
OL,12,Fsaid, 'Yeah, here it is' and gave it
OL,13,Fto him."
OL,15,F"So he doesn't know my name, he didn't
OL,16,Fgive my name on the booking, there
OL,17,Fwere no checks, no questions," says
OL,18,FSarah.
OL,26,@uD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
