PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,FStaff on the desk apologised, and she
OL,8,Fwas offered a partial refund of #70,
OL,9,Fwhich was upped to just over #100
OL,10,Ffollowing Sarah writing a formal
OL,11,Fcomplaint.
OL,13,FBut she says this is not about the
OL,14,Fcost, but rather the principle.
OL,16,F"He saw me naked, and the fact that he
OL,17,Fwas just given this key with such
OL,18,Fease...what was his intention? That is
OL,19,Fsomething that I think about a lot.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F"He shouted at me and told me I was
OL,8,Fsexy. He shouted out my room number.
OL,9,FHe walked downstairs, got a key. What
OL,10,Fwas he hoping to achieve?"
OL,12,FThis incident happened two and a half
OL,13,Fyears after a woman staying at the
OL,14,FTravelodge in Maidenhead was sexually
OL,15,Fassaulted by a man who had lied to
OL,16,Fstaff to get a key to her room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,FUpon reading about the perpetrator's
OL,8,Fhigh-profile conviction in February,
OL,9,FSarah assumed this had happened after
OL,10,Fher traumatic experience, only to
OL,11,Flearn it was not.
OL,13,FI asked her how she felt discovering
OL,14,Fthe Maidenhead crime happened in
OL,15,FDecember 2022, years after her
OL,16,Fincident: "I just sobbed."
OL,18,F"I sobbed because I feel for that
OL,19,Fwoman, because not only did she go
OL,20,Fthrough something horrific, but no
OL,21,Flessons were learned from it. Why?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F"Why was that allowed to happen? Why
OL,8,Fdidn't they even ask what's her name
OL,9,Fon the booking, you know, oh, let's
OL,10,Fjust type in that room and see who's
OL,11,Fthere - small things; this is a basic
OL,12,Frequirement. I've locked the door in
OL,13,Fmy hotel room. I should be safe, and I
OL,14,Fwasn't."
OL,16,FSarah is now one of a growing list of
OL,17,Fwomen pursuing legal claims against
OL,18,Fthe corporation and other hotels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
