SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,FTravelodge have admitted their room
OL,8,Faccess security policies were not
OL,9,Fsufficient at the time of these
OL,10,Fincidents.
OL,12,FWe understand the member of staff
OL,13,Finvolved in what happened to Sarah no
OL,14,Flonger works for the business.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
