PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,FIn a statement, Travelodge told us:
OL,8,F"We are very sorry for this customer's
OL,9,Fexperience. Any case of an
OL,10,Funauthorised person entering a guest's
OL,11,Froom is a significant cause for
OL,12,Fconcern, and we want to be clear that
OL,13,Fthis should not have happened ` our
OL,14,Froom access security policies at the
OL,15,Ftime were not correctly followed,
OL,16,Fwhich is not acceptable.
OL,18,F"We would like to apologise again to
OL,19,Fthe customer for their experience with
OL,20,Fus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
