OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F"We have recently made changes to
OL,8,Fstrengthen our room access security
OL,9,Fpolicies and incident escalation
OL,10,Fprocedures. This includes ensuring
OL,11,Fthat any additional or replacement
OL,12,Froom keys are only issued with
OL,13,Fexplicit permission from the person
OL,14,F(or people) staying in the room, and
OL,15,Fthis has been rolled out to all of our
OL,16,Fhotels, supported by training on our
OL,17,Froom access security and check-in
OL,18,Fprocedures for our 12,000 customer-
OL,19,Ffacing colleagues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F"We have also commissioned an
OL,8,Findependent review led by Paul Greaney
OL,9,FKC, a leading barrister specialising
OL,10,Fin public inquiries concerning
OL,11,Fsecurity, serious violent crime, and
OL,12,Fhealth and safety, to examine our room
OL,13,Faccess security policies and
OL,14,Fescalation procedures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
