PN,30516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778091067
OL,3,CWoman traumatised after man who
OL,4,Charassed her accessed Travelodge hotel
OL,5,Croom
OL,7,F"In parallel to the independent
OL,8,Freview, which is underway, we are
OL,9,Fworking at pace on a further internal
OL,10,Freview of our room access security
OL,11,Fprocesses and training, including
OL,12,Fworking with a leading violence
OL,13,Fagainst women and girls expert, to
OL,14,Fensure our guests are safe and feel
OL,15,Fsafe in our hotels."
OL,17,FThey tell us their external review is
OL,18,Fprogressing at pace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
